description:
Darkness Radio is Remembering A UFO Researcher: Saying Goodbye To Butch Witkowski.

Last week, beloved UFO and Cryptid researcher Butch Witkowski passed away. Darkness Radio assembled two of his best friends in the field, Cryptozoologist Eric Altman and Paranormal Investigator Lon Strickler to recall the life and stories of Butch and talk about specific cases they had been on...
